{"tid":1812833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[有片]便衣同速龍雙雙中椒！","createTime":"2020-01-05T19:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T04:18:28.000Z","uid":274161,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bb3e77db746a31e5e23f7fa55ef20d0ea4268aca","tid":1812833,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T19:42:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KqRrSFgPv7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKqRrSFgPv7c&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1Vlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=6e0e5f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KqRrSFgPv7c</a><br />\n上水遊行結束後不久，警即展開大圍捕，在商場先後制服近百人，又衝入商場驅散市民，情況混亂。在上水中心，一名婦人不滿指罵警員衝入商場「發爛」，亂捉年輕人，有防暴警員向市民噴胡椒噴霧。<br />\n其間，一名便裝蒙面警員多次誤中胡椒噴霧，面露痛苦表情。他及後出示委任證向同袍表明身份，防暴警終停止噴椒，而現場所見，其他警員則沒有出示委任證。中椒的警務人員隨後由兩名蒙面便衣警攙扶離開商場，坐在商場外的花槽治理，現場有響亮喝倒采聲音，也有陣陣歡呼聲傳出。在場另有兩名「速龍」亦疑中椒，狀甚痛苦，需用清水和生理鹽水洗眼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Background_IyiGj_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FBackground_IyiGj_1200x0.png&h=8e81416a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fsin8-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/81529142_1088437461548576_5814417594500775936_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQkgXA7JUBVQV-78vPhcvTIMtSJC7n2aM4WeZ1tD-SZe910rL1muDEAjHnwLEOauOII&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fsin8-1.fna&amp;oh=dabf8cd6e4cf7ef7d43f0a63da82a06b&amp;oe=5EA6BC0F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fsin8-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F81529142_1088437461548576_5814417594500775936_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQkgXA7JUBVQV-78vPhcvTIMtSJC7n2aM4WeZ1tD-SZe910rL1muDEAjHnwLEOauOII%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fsin8-1.fna%26oh%3Ddabf8cd6e4cf7ef7d43f0a63da82a06b%26oe%3D5EA6BC0F&h=5f276ba8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f075b5e55ef0f3e163ca2d2358884ea5ddcd1172","tid":1812833,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2